Class MultiGraphPanel

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, PointClickedListener

    public class MultiGraphPanel
extends GraphPanel
    MultiGraphPanels draw plots of several variables against a single independent variable. They have contextual menus and toolbar buttons similar to those in PhaseGraphPanel and ComponentGraphPanel. They have dialogs for changing the plot variables, but this feature doesn't appear to work fully yet. Perhaps the MultiPlot2D needs to be updated.
    Author:
    Clinic 08-09, modified by Clinic 10-11, Max Comstock 2013
